messageBody:
Let me first apologize if this group does not allow postings such as
this. I could not find any posting or section in the FAQ that states
solicitation is frowned upon. Let me cut to the chase...

I am a technical recruiter working on a Tester\QA assignment here in
Columbus Ohio that calls for Test Director, Load Runner and J-Unit
experience. Java programming knowledge and testing methodology
needed. If you or someone you might know might be interested in a 4-
5 month assignment, feel free to contact me so I can provide further
information.

Thank You,
